	   <tr><td colspan=2>I agree with all the suggestions so far.&nbsp;&nbsp;I would only add this, mix it up!!  Start out snareing and bow kiting the MOB to soften them up.  You can mix it some of you DD spells while bow kiting.  When the MOB is to 1/2 or less HP go in there and tank it.  Try to stick either to animals you can hit with panic animal/snare when you tank so you take less damage or fight MOBS that are cowards and try to run when low on HP.  This also helps ya take less damage.  The undead suck cause they usually stay & fight to the bitter end!!  Good luck and good hunting!!<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
